&lt;p&gt;The Account Manager – Professional Liability is responsible for managing client relationships for Professional Liability policies and ensuring customer satisfaction, retention, and growth. This role includes servicing accounts, handling renewals, processing new business, and maintaining accurate client data.&lt;/p&gt;
