&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Client Management&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage relationships for clients with Professional Liability policies (MedPro, Dentist Advantage, E&amp;amp;S)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain high levels of customer satisfaction and support agency retention goals&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
