&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proactively manage assigned client relationships to ensure satisfaction and retention&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain regular client contact based on individual account needs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Respond promptly to client calls and emails&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Address client questions, concerns, and service requests in a timely manner&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage all policy renewals beginning at least 90 days prior to expiration&lt;/li&gt;
