&lt;li&gt;Manage the full lifecycle of new business from application through binding&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Policy Servicing &amp;amp; Administration&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Enter and maintain accurate client data in agency management systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Process policy changes, endorsements, and updates as requested by clients&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure all work is completed accurately and in compliance with internal procedures&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow all agency workflows and procedures&lt;/li&gt;
