&lt;p&gt;There are many reasons why EPIC Insurance Brokers &amp;amp; Consultants has become one of the fastest-growing firms in the insurance industry. Fueled and driven by capable, committed people who share common beliefs and values and “bring it” every day, EPIC is always looking for people who have “the right stuff” – people who know what they want and aren’t afraid to make it happen.&lt;/p&gt;
